front.title: •Han's Toolkit
front.gametext: Use 1 Force to deploy on one of you characters, vehicles or starships (free on Falcon or Han). While aboard a vehicle or starship, you may use 1 Force to cancel any Interrupt or Effect of any kind (except those immune to Alter or Control) which targets that vehicle or starship.
front.lore: Experienced pilots keep a well equipped toolkit. Horizontal boosters, alluvial dampers and hydrospanners aid in performing high-tech repairs aboard starships.

canceledBy: Turn It Off! Turn It Off!
cancels: Any Interrupt or Effect of any kind which targets this vehicle or starship
